\nw[\N[21]]The ground stopped moving... and it turned into
something normal too...

\nw[\N[1]]The core is completely gone. We defeated the Earth
Beast!

\nw[\N[3]]We were able to protect the town. I finally feel
like I've been able to repay the favor.

\nw[\N[21]]Ah, we did it. I've been saved by Prae so many
times, but finally...!

\nw[\N[21]]This isn't the time to celebrate. Our job isn't
done until we safely return.

\nw[\N[21]]The Earth Beast might cause something to happen
when it returns to a normal mountain. Let's escape
as soon as possible!

Congratulations on clearing. After clearing, you
will be able to do things similar to
intermissions, which is behind the scenes.

When you want to see the ending, you can talk to
Louis after fulfilling the conditions to watch it.

You can view memories by moving from the blue
circle in the room to the flashback room.

I would be happy if you could enjoy the exclusive
events after clearing.
